==============
README: PetIGA
==============

:Authors:      Lisandro Dalcin, Nathaniel Collier
:Contact:      dalcinl@gmail.com, nathaniel.collier@gmail.com
:Institutions: CONICET_, KAUST_

.. _CONICET:  http://www.conicet.gov.ar/
.. _KAUST:    http://www.kaust.edu.sa/

This software framework implements a NURBS-based Galerkin finite
element method (FEM), popularly known as *isogeometric analysis*
(IGA). It is heavily based on PETSc_, the *Portable, Extensible
Toolkit for Scientific Computation*.

.. _PETSc:  http://www.mcs.anl.gov/petsc/
